      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta diwipadefmits trescha\nMaëfiotam/ lihdsar winna Deh-\nleem un ar winna Brahteem/ to\nbija diwipadefmits."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta diwidesmits zettorta\nRomanti-Eezeram/lihdsar win-\nna Dehleem un ar winna Brah-\nteem/ to bija diwipadefmits."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N to Wahrtu-Sargu Kahrtu bija fchi: No\nteein Koriteeem bija Meseleimjus Korus Dehls no\nAffaiva Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Meselemijus Behrni\nbfja: Sakarijs tas pirmdsim-\nnis/ Jediaëls tas ehtrajs/ Se-\nbadijus tas treschajs/ Jatnïels\ntas zettortajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Elains tas peektajs/ Joka-\nnans tas festajs/ Elioenajus tas\nfeptitajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Obed-Eedomam bija\narridsan Behrni: Semajus tas\npirmdsimnis/ Josabads tas oh-\ntrajs/ Joaks tas treschajs/ un\nSakars tas zettortajs/ un Ne-\ntaneëls tas peektajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Amniëls tas festajs/ Ih-\nsachars tas feptitajs/ Pegulta-\njus tas astotajs/ jo Deews bij\nwinnu swehtijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna Dehlam Sema-\njam dfinme arridsan Dehli/ kas\nfawa Tehwa Namma waldisa/\njo tee bija stipri warrent Wihti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Semajus Behrni bija At-\nnus/ un Rewaëls/ un Obeds/\nun Efsabads winna Brahti tik-\nkuschti Wihri/ Elijus un Sema-\nkijus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee wiffi bija no Obed-\nEedoma Behrneem/ tik labbi pa-\ntchi/ ka winnu Behrnt/ un win-\nnu Brahti stipri Wihri/ tikkus-\nchi pee Kalpochanas feschdef-\nmits diwi no Obed-Eedoma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Meseleinjam bija Behr-\nni un Brahti/ tikkuschi Wihr-\nastonpadefmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Offami no Merara\nBehrneem bija Dehli/ Simrus\ntas Wirfneeks/ jepfchu wiisch-\ntas pirmdsimnis ue bija/tatschu\nwinna Tehws to eezeble par\nWirfneeku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ilkijus bija tas ehtrajs/\nTebaltjus tas treschajs/ Saka-\nrius tas zettortajs/ wiffu Offa\nBehrnu un Brahtu bija trihs-\npadefmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No scheein tappe par\nWahrtu-Sargeeu nodalliti/\nstarp to warrenu Wihtu Wirf-\nneekeem pee Kalpochanas/ lihds\nar faween Brahteem/ ta KUR-\nGA Namuna kalpoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee mesflojahstif labbi\npar masu ka par leelu/ starp fa-\nwn Tehwu Nammu/ pee itkat-\nrahm Wahrtim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta Mesflochanas Sih-\nme prett Rihteem tappe Mesele-\nmijam/ bet winna Dehlam Sa-\nkarijam/ kas weens gudrs Pa-\ndohmadeweis bija/ tappe mef-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
